Components:
  Custom Objects:
    QuickNotes__c
    Fields:
      Record_Id__c - Text field
      Notes__c - Rich Text area
  LWC:
    quickNotes.html
    quickNotes.css
    quickNotes.js
    quickNotes.js-meta.xml
  Apex Class:
    QuickNotesController.cls
    QuickNotesController.cls-meta.xml
    
Place the LWC on any record detail Page
Notes get saved into QuickNotes custom object with record Id and Notes
On MouseOut the Upsert notes is called
On emptying out the notes the record is deleted from Quick Notes
Max character count on Notes is 32768
Characters left are shown at the bottom of the Notes Component
